message.body: I can do tomorrow instead of Saturday if you want to
That'd be cool. Get started at 8?

We just gotta set these windows real plumb and seal them up. One will need the sill planed a little and one needs some exterior trim messed with. If we get done early and you want more hours we can set some joists too but it's up to you.
What is your rate these days?
No. It's gotta be power planer, which I have. I guess plan on 4 or 5 hrs tomorrow.
I'll bring my hand and cordless tools and level. Anything else I need to bring?
If you're planning to drive just meet me at my place. Parking sucks by the shop.
